<p><a href="#sdfootnote87anc" name="sdfootnote87sym">87</a>In the night time it was easy to spot even a black cat entering the traffic circle. However, in the day time, I never saw any birds sitting on the sculpture, although they would sit on all trees and bushes in the area.</p>
